com.nokia.maps.kml.component

Interface KMLEventListener


  • public interface KMLEventListener
    This interface defines a callback method which is used when the currently focused KML object has changed.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onFocusChanged(Feature feature)
      This method is called whenever the focus of the map has changed from the current <Feature>

      • onFocusChanged

        void onFocusChanged(Feature feature)
        This method is called whenever the focus of the map has changed from the current <Feature>
        Parameters:
        feature - the currently focused <Feature>, or Null if no feature is currently focused upon.
